    AssessmentExecutor<DOC>

    public class BasicAssessmentExecutor<DOC extends Document>
extends AbstractAssessmentExecutor<DOC>
    A basic, non-mutable implementation of an AssessmentExecutor. It evaluates each provided assessment in sequential order.
